DOC.DH:
Nan Koehler brought more than 1,000 babies into the world,
but she stopped after a lawsuit. She agreed to do it one last time;
the infant was born brain-damaged.

DOC.TE:
   When the baby was breathing, Koehler started the second bottle;
but after a few minutes, that one ran out. Koehler told Condon to get
more oxygen at a fire station.

   In spite of all, my magnanimity endured. Anything was better than
the chunder bus. Besides, the Himalayan foothills were approaching;
they were sure to slow Vandan down.

   He also listed food and beverages I should avoid: aged cheese,
such as Parmesan or Gorgonzola; anchovies, sardines and shellfish;
spinach and tomatoes; cured meats, such as salami, prosciutto, ham;
chocolate; and the piece de resistance, wine.

   Rounding out the field are Azure Classic Star; Ferragamo, who
finished third behind He Doll and Hes Spotless three weeks ago;
Crocodile Hunter, Seeks Joy and Rail Skimmer.
